## Project Overview

### Problem Statement
Security professionals often switch between multiple tools during assessments and incident response. There's a need for an intelligent command-line interface that understands security context and can assist with common security operations through AI-powered recommendations.

### Objectives
- Create an AI-integrated command-line shell for security operations
- Implement intelligent command suggestions based on security context
- Build a fast, low-overhead tool in C for system-level performance
- Provide seamless integration with existing security workflows

### Target Users
Security professionals, SOC analysts, and penetration testers who work extensively in terminal environments.

### My Role
Solo developer — Architecture design, C implementation, and AI integration.

